I was very concerned when I saw insects, so thank God it didn't go into super weird territory and just stuck with the normal weird. 4/10. I'm no vanilla fag, and can enjoy some good NTR every now and again, but the drawing is a bit problematic. The art itself isn't the problem, since this looks to be someone starting out which, to there credit, looks quite nice. The problem is that not all of the lines are drawn the same, so some end up lighter shades and end up blending together, so there isn't a lot of separation. The story is nothing spectacular, told through Google lens-sama, it's basically rape for the sake of rape. Though I may be missing details.
I did not understand what was occurring, and I am pleased that I did not, because spiders should not be near pornography.
